<p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.5;" data-mce-style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.5;"><span style="font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 18pt;" data-mce-style="font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 18pt;"> Ano nga ba ang meron sayo?</span></p>
